  "title": "COMMIS CHEF (5 day work week)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Ensure the consistency in the preparation of all food items</li>\n  <li>Maintain proper rotation of product in all chillers to minimize wastage/spoilage</li>\n  <li>Ensure the cleanliness and maintenance of all work areas, utensils, and equipment</li>\n  <li>Follow kitchen policies, procedures and service standards</li>\n  <li>Follow all safety and sanitation policies when handling food and beverage</li>\n  <li>Other duties as assigned</li>\n  <li>Candidate with Basic Food Hygiene Certificate will have higher consideration</li>\n  <li>Experience in F&amp;B industry will be an added advantage</li>\n  <li>Candidates with no experience are welcome to apply</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Good command of spoken English</li>\n  <li>Pleasant and outgoing personality</li>\n  <li>Team player, preferable with good communication and interpersonal skills</li>\n  <li>Positive service attitude, coachable, willingness to learn</li>\n  <li>High standard of personal hygiene</li>\n  <li>Able to work on weekends and public holidays</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>5 day work week</li>\n  <li>Variable Bonus and daily incentive scheme</li>\n  <li>Free shuttle bus from Tanah Merah MRT station</li>\n</ul>",
